---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import Header from '../../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../../components/Footer.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Other Key Projects | CP Systems">
  <Header />

  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="project-hero animate-on-scroll">
    <div class="project-hero__bg">
      <img src="/images/other_projects/tapovan_1.jpg" alt="Other Key Projects" />
      <div class="project-hero__overlay"></div>
    </div>
    <div class="container project-hero__content">
      <div class="project-hero__badge">Project Gallery</div>
      <h1 class="project-hero__title">Other Key Projects</h1>
      <p class="project-hero__subtitle">Showcasing our diverse portfolio of critical infrastructure rehabilitation, grouting, and structural enhancements across India.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Project Details Matrix -->
  <section class="project-info section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="project-info__grid">
        <div class="project-info__item animate-on-scroll">
          <div class="project-info__label">Category</div>
          <div class="project-info__value">Hydropower & Infrastructure</div>
        </div>
        <div class="project-info__item animate-on-scroll" style="transition-delay: 0.1s;">
          <div class="project-info__label">Locations</div>
          <div class="project-info__value">Uttarakhand, J&K, MP</div>
        </div>
        <div class="project-info__item animate-on-scroll" style="transition-delay: 0.2s;">
          <div class="project-info__label">Status</div>
          <div class="project-info__value">Successfully Delivered</div>
        </div>
        <div class="project-info__item animate-on-scroll" style="transition-delay: 0.3s;">
          <div class="project-info__label">Scope</div>
          <div class="project-info__value">Rehabilitation, Grouting, Stabilization</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Tapovan -->
  <section class="project-overview section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-header animate-on-scroll">
        <h2 class="section-title">Tapovan Vishnugad HPP</h2>
        <div class="section-divider"></div>
        <p class="section-subtitle">Repair & Rectification of RC Dam Structure, Rebaring, and Micro Concreting.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="content-text animate-on-scroll">
        <p>This critical infrastructure project involved comprehensive repair and structural reinforcement of the dam RC components. The scope included removal of loose concrete, advanced rebaring using couplers and shear connectors, and supplying/applying high-strength micro-concrete and epoxy mortars to ensure the longevity of the structure.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="project-gallery">
        <div class="gallery-item"><img src="/images/other_projects/tapovan_1.jpg" alt="Tapovan Structure Repair" /><span class="gallery-caption">Repair & Rectification</span></div>
        <div class="gallery-item"><img src="/images/other_projects/tapovan_2.jpg" alt="Damaged Concrete Removal" /><span class="gallery-caption">Loose Concrete Removal</span></div>
        <div class="gallery-item"><img src="/images/other_projects/tapovan_3.jpg" alt="Rebaring" /><span class="gallery-caption">Rebaring & Strengthening</span></div>
        <div class="gallery-item"><img src="/images/other_projects/tapovan_4.jpg" alt="Couplers" /><span class="gallery-caption">Coupler & Shear Connectors</span></div>
        <div class="gallery-item"><img src="/images/other_projects/tapovan_5.jpg" alt="Micro Concreting" /><span class="gallery-caption">Micro Concreting</span></div>
        <div class="gallery-item"><img src="/images/other_projects/tapovan_6.jpg" alt="Completed Repair" /><span class="gallery-caption">Strengthened RC Structure</span></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Maneri Bhali -->
  <section class="project-overview section section--beige">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-header animate-on-scroll">
        <h2 class="section-title">Maneri Bhali Stage-I Dam</h2>
        <div class="section-divider"></div>
        <p class="section-subtitle">Special repair of spillway and roller bucket.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="content-text animate-on-scroll">
        <p>Faced with heavily damaged seal beams, severe silt erosion, and deep cavities, CP Systems executed highly complex underwater repairs in the lean season. The works involved profile matching with high-performance M80 concrete, rebaring, epoxy grouting, and laying MS plate liners for the spillway and roller buckets.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="project-gallery mt-4">
        <div class="gallery-item"><img src="/images/other_projects/maneri_bhali_1.jpg" alt="Spillway Repair" /><span class="gallery-caption">Spillway Reinforcement</span></div>
        <div class="gallery-item"><img src="/images/other_projects/maneri_bhali_2.jpg" alt="Construction Progress" /><span class="gallery-caption">Profile Restructuring</span></div>
        <div class="gallery-item"><img src="/images/other_projects/maneri_bhali_3.jpg" alt="Roller Bucket Repair" /><span class="gallery-caption">Roller Bucket Treatment</span></div>
        <div class="gallery-item"><img src="/images/other_projects/maneri_bhali_4.jpg" alt="Completed Works" /><span class="gallery-caption">Advanced Rebaring</span></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Koteshwar HEP -->
  <section class="project-overview section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-header animate-on-scroll">
        <h2 class="section-title">Koteshwar Hydroelectric Project</h2>
        <div class="section-divider"></div>
        <p class="section-subtitle">Slope stabilization, shotcreting, and advanced structural grouting.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="content-text animate-on-scroll">
        <p>Spanning 36 months, this monumental execution involved stabilization of the left bank reaching heights of 200m from the river bed. Over 20,000 sqm area was secured via rock-bolting and chainlink. Furthermore, the power intake, turbine base plates, and construction joints were rigorously treated with extensive Epoxy and PU grouting.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="project-gallery mt-4">
        <div class="gallery-item"><img src="/images/other_projects/koteshwar_1.jpg" alt="Slope Stabilization" /><span class="gallery-caption">Extensive Slope Stabilization</span></div>
        <div class="gallery-item"><img src="/images/other_projects/koteshwar_2.jpg" alt="Shotcreting" /><span class="gallery-caption">Wet Shotcrete & Anchoring</span></div>
        <div class="gallery-item"><img src="/images/other_projects/koteshwar_3.jpg" alt="Epoxy Mortar Treatment" /><span class="gallery-caption">Epoxy Mortar Treatment</span></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- VPHEP Pipalkoti Grouting -->
  <section class="project-overview section section--beige">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-header animate-on-scroll">
        <h2 class="section-title">VPHEP Pipalkoti - TBM Grouting</h2>
        <div class="section-divider"></div>
        <p class="section-subtitle">Consolidation of fragile strata using Polyurethane and Colloidal Silica.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="content-text animate-on-scroll">
        <p>In 2021, the VPHEP Tunnel Boring Machine (TBM) was stuck in the highly fragile HRT section. Over a span of 1.5 years, CP Systems executed intricate consolidation drilling and PU/Microfine cement grouting to completely stabilize the sandy strata and successfully release the TBM.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="project-gallery mt-4">
        <div class="gallery-item"><img src="/images/other_projects/pipalkoti_grouting_1.png" alt="TBM Grouting" /><span class="gallery-caption">PU Consolidation Grouting</span></div>
        <div class="gallery-item"><img src="/images/other_projects/pipalkoti_grouting_2.jpg" alt="Colloidal Silica" /><span class="gallery-caption">Colloidal Silica Treatment</span></div>
        <div class="gallery-item"><img src="/images/other_projects/pipalkoti_grouting_3.jpg" alt="Fragile Strata" /><span class="gallery-caption">Fragile HRT Strata</span></div>
        <div class="gallery-item"><img src="/images/other_projects/pipalkoti_grouting_4.jpg" alt="PU Pumping" /><span class="gallery-caption">High-Pressure PU Injection</span></div>
        <div class="gallery-item"><img src="/images/other_projects/pipalkoti_grouting_5.jpg" alt="Consolidation Operations" /><span class="gallery-caption">TBM Surrounding Consolidation</span></div>
        <div class="gallery-item"><img src="/images/other_projects/pipalkoti_grouting_6.jpg" alt="TBM Release" /><span class="gallery-caption">Successful Stabilization</span></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Sewa II HEP -->
  <section class="project-overview section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-header animate-on-scroll">
        <h2 class="section-title">Sewa II HEP (J&K)</h2>
        <div class="section-divider"></div>
        <p class="section-subtitle">HRT repair with Epoxy Mortar and severe leakage stoppage.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="content-text animate-on-scroll">
        <p>Executed in 2010 across a challenging 10-kilometer-long, 3.3m diameter tunnel. Operations required massive logistical feats to manually transport heavy machinery deep into the tunnel from limited entry points. The persistent severe headwater leakages were fully addressed through focused PU grouting and epoxy treatments.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="project-gallery mt-4">
        <div class="gallery-item"><img src="/images/other_projects/sewa_1.jpg" alt="Sewa II HRT" /><span class="gallery-caption">Sewa II HRT Repair</span></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Misc Infra Projects -->
  <section class="project-overview section section--beige" style="padding-bottom: 80px;">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-header animate-on-scroll">
        <h2 class="section-title">Other Notable Infrastructure Developments</h2>
        <div class="section-divider"></div>
        <p class="section-subtitle">Decades of expertise spanning expressways, pipelines, and thermal power across the country.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="content-text animate-on-scroll" style="margin-top: 2rem;">
        <ul style="list-style-type: none; padding: 0; display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr)); gap: 15px;">
          <li style="background: var(--white); padding: 15px 20px; border-radius: var(--radius); box-shadow: var(--shadow-sm); border-left: 4px solid var(--gold);"><strong style="color:var(--navy);">Nagpur-Mumbai Expressway:</strong> Passive Fire Protection (Pkg 14).</li>
          <li style="background: var(--white); padding: 15px 20px; border-radius: var(--radius); box-shadow: var(--shadow-sm); border-left: 4px solid var(--gold);"><strong style="color:var(--navy);">Rajpura Thermal Power:</strong> Civil, grading, minor bridge execution.</li>
          <li style="background: var(--white); padding: 15px 20px; border-radius: var(--radius); box-shadow: var(--shadow-sm); border-left: 4px solid var(--gold);"><strong style="color:var(--navy);">Nagloi CETP:</strong> High-capacity structural treatments (12 & 24 MLD).</li>
          <li style="background: var(--white); padding: 15px 20px; border-radius: var(--radius); box-shadow: var(--shadow-sm); border-left: 4px solid var(--gold);"><strong style="color:var(--navy);">GAIL Gas Pipeline:</strong> 294km joint coating from Jaipur to Loni.</li>
          <li style="background: var(--white); padding: 15px 20px; border-radius: var(--radius); box-shadow: var(--shadow-sm); border-left: 4px solid var(--gold);"><strong style="color:var(--navy);">HMEL Bhatinda Refinery:</strong> Specialized insulation deployment.</li>
          <li style="background: var(--white); padding: 15px 20px; border-radius: var(--radius); box-shadow: var(--shadow-sm); border-left: 4px solid var(--gold);"><strong style="color:var(--navy);">AIIMS Bhopal:</strong> PU Foam Insulation and PVC membrane waterproofing.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <Footer />
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  /* Hero Section */
  .project-hero {
    position: relative;
    height: 50vh;
    min-height: 400px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    color: var(--white);
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .project-hero__bg {
    position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; width: 100%; height: 100%; z-index: -1;
  }
  .project-hero__bg img {
    width: 100%; height: 100%; object-fit: cover;
  }
  .project-hero__overlay {
    position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; width: 100%; height: 100%;
    background: linear-gradient(to right, rgba(12,35,64,0.95), rgba(12,35,64,0.4));
  }
  .project-hero__content {
    position: relative; z-index: 1; max-width: 800px;
  }
  .project-hero__badge {
    display: inline-block;
    padding: 6px 16px;
    background: rgba(255,180,0,0.2);
    border: 1px solid var(--gold);
    color: var(--gold);
    border-radius: 20px;
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 1px;
  }
  .project-hero__title {
    font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 5vw, 4rem);
    font-weight: 800;
    line-height: 1.1;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }
  .project-hero__subtitle {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.9);
    line-height: 1.6;
    max-width: 600px;
  }

  /* Info Grid */
  .project-info {
    background: var(--white);
    padding: 40px 0;
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
  }
  .project-info__grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(200px, 1fr));
    gap: 30px;
  }
  .project-info__item {
    padding-left: 20px;
    border-left: 3px solid var(--gold);
  }
  .project-info__label {
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    color: var(--grey-text);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 1px;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
    font-weight: 600;
  }
  .project-info__value {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--navy);
  }
  
  .section--beige {
    background: var(--beige);
  }

  .content-text {
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    color: var(--dark-text);
    line-height: 1.8;
    max-width: 900px;
  }
  
  .mt-4 {
    margin-top: 2.5rem;
  }

  /* Gallery Grid Matches Other Pages */
  .project-gallery {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(300px, 1fr));
    gap: 20px;
    margin-top: 40px;
  }
  .gallery-item { border-radius: var(--radius); overflow: hidden; position: relative; box-shadow: var(--shadow-md); }
  .gallery-item img { width: 100%; height: 240px; object-fit: cover; transition: transform 0.4s ease; }
  .gallery-item:hover img { transform: scale(1.05); }
  .gallery-caption {
    display: block; padding: 8px 12px; font-size: 0.8rem; color: #000;
    text-align: center; background: var(--white); font-weight: 500;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .project-info__grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; }
  }
</style>
